{
  "stem": "1721.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Russians were then in control.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Again a lot of what I'm hearing-- a lot of my recollection is sort of muddy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I don't know if I recalled it exactly at the time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Was it my independent recollection at the time I was there?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or did I hear about it later, and did I associate it with the time I was there?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I know one recollection I had-- and again, I don't know at what point it was-- where there were rumors floating around that this camp was going to be liquidated, eliminated, whether it was going to be they were building gas chambers, or they were going to move us out.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was probably somewhere about March, April when the Germans realized that the tide was turning.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they really had to get rid of a lot of inmates.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was a rumor floating around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know if I heard about it later, or if I heard about it at the time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I, I don't know what the reaction was, but it was definitely information that was coming through that they were building gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Or either building them or preparing for us for them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I don't recall how I felt at the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean, I remember hearing about this thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I don't know if I-- if I felt close enough to associate myself with it at the time, at that point.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We may have been just so beaten down that, you know, it may just have been another phase of our lives.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But anyway, in May-- first week, second week of May.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "First week of May, I believe, is the Soviets came.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But it was pretty close.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
